::Striker::

Striker turns his head as he hears a whisper, surprized to see Spears looking 
at him through a hole in the door. His internal systems reported that his 
shoulder blasters were almost reactivated. His jetpack, though, would take 
slightly more time.

"What's going on?" he asks Spears, remembering the chip that was shot at her 
before he went into stasis lock.
